c=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來漢奸黎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要捉佢啲女去補償民族創傷"},{"pid":"47707e4a66bb4da2ba27a135e0540f1d1f631828","tid":2037760,"uid":203961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8e7af32f5f0186a23331b7a8ed01e5b68c6079c6","tid":2037760,"uid":4052,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"8311b2c4b496fa9afcc6ac2a7c190f2ce3f1a951","tid":2037760,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"63acaed967cd72571913a79a71a4f5519297d73a","tid":2037760,"uid":102701,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"1941年，香港島上的戰爭氣氛越來越濃，每 天不斷有難民擁入。戰爭一觸即發，大學是讀不下去了，個人前途渺茫，家庭生活壓力這麼大，不如到澳門去博一下。第二天，何鴻燊揣著10元港幣--那是他在 報警室工作8天所得的津貼，擠上一艘開往澳門的小艇，在爭搶著逃離香港的難民堆中駛向未知的明天。<br />\n<br />\n我都係見個網講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://articles.zkiz.com/?rbid=24132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farticles.zkiz.com%2F%3Frbid%3D24132&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=ec070956\" target=\"_blank\">https://articles.zkiz.com/?rbid=24132</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:06:43.000Z","msg":"10元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T09:09:12.000Z","msg":"佢就係用呢10蚊喺賭船度羸咗2千5百萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d2c2a7f207484ebbde5923b96ec3744a5309167","tid":2037760,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d965eaafe1ff54a7fbbf4644f8ab4a15ea0fe21a","tid":2037760,"uid":130595,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b9d3b68afa97c55f8113c2c9e31fffe05e9fb34f","tid":2037760,"uid":102701,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"b5997e